[name]
check_mailq

[info]
Checks the number of mails in the mailq on unix mailsystems.
[why]
To catch problems with the mail system.
[how]
Searches through the mailq and lets you specify minimum and maximum allowed mails in the queue. Supports sendmail, qmail, postfix and exim.
[platforms]
Unix

